						<summary>

						<p>States that while <hi rend="bold">Chōḍamahārāja</hi> was ruling the <hi rend="bold">Rēnāṇḍu seven thousand</hi> a certain <hi rend="bold">Bhikirāju</hi> made a gift of one hundred and twenty <hi rend="italic">maṟutus</hi> of land fetching twelve <hi rend="italic">puṭṭis</hi> of paddy to a certain Śaivite mendicant <hi rend="bold">Apimana-Gorava.</hi></p>						

